Hey all, as a 3rd map made for Project-MP is this the newest Bluemoon.
It's called like it because many blue-colored textures are in that map and alot of blue light.

This map includes -
ANTI-AFK
42 CT Spawns
2 T Spawns
4 secrets / nades
Teleports
17 Traps
Awp, BHOP, Knife ending

* New 3 songs added on the end press the button to play the music ! *
* New Self made objects added to grenades ! *

I hope that you enjoy the map ! Made by Cheap Shot, www.project-mp.com
